									BIG (Big Is Gem) 1.80
									
									
BIG is a library of fuctions to enhance GEM. It contains functions for :
		
		- Shortkeys in dialogs and menus;
		- Movable dialogs;
		- Dialogs in windows;
		- Popups menus;
		- Hierachicals Menus;
		- Menus and TOOLBARs in windows;
		- And more ...

BIG can handle the BIGgest part of the work with windows.

The library is designed for the PURE C compiler.

The documentation and the library is in french but an english version will 
come.

A demo program is included.

The author (Claude Attard) adress can be found in the documentation file :
	Big.txt
	
This library is freeware.
